## Limitations
This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest research findings. The lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the currency of the information. Additionally, the report does not delve into the socio-economic factors that might influence access to and participation in competitive sports for children. Further research, including longitudinal studies, would be beneficial to understand the long-term impacts of competitive sports on children's development.

